            <a href="https://npc.collegeboard.org/app/soka?iframe=true" target="">Get Your Financial Aid Estimate!</a>
      
  
    </h3>

      <div  class="gen-block__body">
        
            <p>View your estimated financial aid at SUA.</p>
      
  
    </div>


