            <div class="wysiwyg paragraph paragraph--type-wysiwyg paragraph--view-mode-default ds-1col clearfix">

  

  <div class="wysiwyg__content">
          <div  class="wysiwyg__body">
        
            <h2>Important Notes</h2>

<ul>
	<li>Calculations are based upon a full-time undergraduate student entering classes in Fall 2020.</li>
	<li>This calculator estimates financial aid eligibility for Soka University of America merit-based and need-based aid, as well as federal student aid.</li>
	<li>The results are dependent upon the accuracy and completeness of the information you submit.&nbsp;</li>
	<li>The results are an estimate that is based upon 2020-2021&nbsp;Soka University of America costs. Results do not represent any guarantee of the final cost, or your actual financial aid award. Your actual financial aid eligibility will be determined by the Soka University Office of Financial Aid&nbsp;and will require you to complete an official&nbsp;financial aid application.</li>
</ul>

      
  
